### **MODULE 1: Introduction to Linux**
- **What is Linux?** â€“ Open-source OS kernel created by Linus Torvalds in 1991.  
- **GNU/Linux vs Unix** â€“ Unix is proprietary (Solaris, AIX), GNU/Linux is free & open-source.  
- **Open Source Licensing** â€“ GPL ensures software is free to use, modify, distribute.  
